com.isti.traceview.data
Class PlotDataPoint

java.lang.Object
  com.isti.traceview.data.PlotDataPoint
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class PlotDataPoint
extends Object
implements Serializable

represents one screen point of graph, contains all data needed to draw pixel. Each point on screen graph represents some time range of raw trace data. Data point in this case is a vertical line from minimal to maximal value for representing time range.

Author:
Max Kokoulin
